You need to adjust the height of it,
你得把高度调整一下，

189
00:08:54.700 --> 00:08:56.276
and you just do it by shrugging.
耸耸肩就可以。

190
00:08:56.300 --> 00:08:58.196
(Laughter)
（笑声）

